Class BasicMap<T1,T2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.utils.BasicMap<T1,T2>
  • Type Parameters:
    T1 - keys
    T2 - values

    public class BasicMap<T1,T2>
extends java.lang.Object
    An extremely simple map implementation that doesn't require both parameters to have valid hashcode/equals. Simply 2 lists that that have the key/value at the same index in each other.
    Author:
    Timothy
